sources.title: Phantom Ranger
sources.description: A Treasury Department engraver is being held captive by a counterfeiting gang that wants him to make counterfeit plates for them. A lawman is sent to rescue him.

sources.title: Phantom Ranger (1938) TIM McCOY
sources.description:
Stars: Tim McCoy, Suzanne Kaaren, Karl Hackett 
Director: Sam Newfield

When a Treasury Department engraver is being held captive by a gang counterfeiters, a lawman is sent to rescue him.

metadata.Plot: Sharpe has kidnaped an engraver and is flooding the country with counterfeit bills. The FBI spots a town in miniature on a bill and sends in Tim Hayes. Tim starts out by robbing Sharpe's men of the phony bills. Then he enters as a friend proposing to get rid of the money for Sharpe but instead planning to bring in his men to round them up.
metadata.Actors: Tim McCoy, Suzanne Kaaren, Karl Hackett
